

---
import PublicationLayout from "../../layouts/PublicationLayout.astro";

const title = "Books";
const description = "Long-form work extending beyond the page.";
---

<PublicationLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
>
  <section class="publication" data-pagefind-body>

    <h1>Exit Wounds</h1>

    <p>
      A collection of poetry exploring recovery, identity, and the mechanics of breaking patterns that reinforce harm. The work traces a toxic relationship with both a person and a substance, alongside a period of homelessness captured in pieces like “Room 223” and “11am.” Written to move from observation to agency.
    </p>

    <blockquote>
      I poured from a well he never meant to fill.
      <br /><br />
      I called it love.
      <br /><br />
      I called it patience.
      <br /><br />
      I did not yet have the language for loss that arrives before departure.
    </blockquote>

    <p class="meta">
      Independent publisher · Paperback · eBook
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Available on Amazon
      </a>
    </p>

  </section>
</PublicationLayout>